    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i haven't been able to pick up a brush in months. it's like the part of me that actually sees color and light is just... gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore. just this empty, quiet shell of someone who used to matter. it feels like there's nothing left inside.",
