      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like i'm just \"losing my way\" though. it feels like the actual substance of me has evaporated. like the person who could feel things, create things, even just *be*... that person is dead. and now i'm just stuck inhabiting this heavy, useless anatomy that's just taking up space. it's like being a haunted house with no ghost inside. just an empty building waiting to be torn down.",
